3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"樓主有無諗過點解要唱歌、搞黃圈、保育等等嘅文化野？<br />\n因為人對一個地方有身份認同先會對果個地方付出，覺得自己唔係屬於果個地方嘅人咪會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91c3b55dde89076ad5ea351a75f7c30317df2aa","tid":2020511,"uid":10241,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"香港是我家<br />\n家人朋友係晒度<br />\n再講走去第2度又點,始終沒屋企既感覺<br />\n如果走去第2度然後又有野,唔通我再走去第3個地方咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己可以話走就走<br />\n但我屋企人唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c72d50467697fd7a7799bbeffc3e55504946d0","tid":2020511,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"生於斯 長於斯"},{"pid":"0702a461dfafaf0faafac4df27fc47b142c182dd","tid":2020511,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d9c72d50467697fd7a7799bbeffc3e55504946d0","tid":2020511,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"生於斯 長於斯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚天真嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f23d3d294e2d21bda4b3b5acc186aeec6c6b3b5","tid":2020511,"uid":209644,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"92b38bf76255edfc289e46b10d0a64b4792d7bef","tid":2020511,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"有得走邊個唔想走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"大部分人的心聲"},{"pid":"14f232e135ecbe88ccd7c21b4931fcd7494d8101","tid":2020511,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢度係我地嘅地方"},{"pid":"8785d4508870575ac6d8d978ff4b35ae4a9fd86e","tid":2020511,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"供樓30年"},{"pid":